      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOT TO TRACE (2) flew the lids with a fast early split last time, hitting the frame with a 5.5 lengths second (22.97) over 400m at this track and making it two placings on end. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Likely to be in the finish again. SAMARA ROSE (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (18.29) in a Maiden at Taree Super Track. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Should be in this for a long way. ZIPPING SHYANN (8) finished midfield on debut when fifth (23.53) at this track over 400m. Can find the frame this time. MYLA CARGO (7) warrants respect although new to this track.",
